  "detailed_description": "<br>The Arctic has always been a mysterious place. Running a motel in the Arctic is also a rare experience. Through the Arctic Motel Simulator, we not only want to simulate the climate and changeable weather of the Arctic, but also want to bring an Arctic-style motel management experience. This is reflected in the following aspects:<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/fd14c06e686734b9e0674cfa937ae236.avif?t=1771944935\" width=320 height=64 /></span><br>The Arctic is a vast and sparsely populated place. In the game, you will be able to expand the territory of the motel in the primeval forest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/561ef9912a23850e812a3c15c8b5a1fe.poster.avif?t=1771944935\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/561ef9912a23850e812a3c15c8b5a1fe.webm?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/561ef9912a23850e812a3c15c8b5a1fe.mp4?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/403a86b3b6367ec57ba1d8f5d83aaaee.avif?t=1771944935\" width=320 height=64 /></span><br>It is not easy to find a motel in the Arctic. Motels there often provide many different types of services. In addition to providing various types of rooms for rent, shops selling Arctic specialties and restaurants offering Arctic cuisine can also earn you a lot of money. There are more, including laundries and other businesses waiting for you to discover.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/be688b0e77450707749a3504d717641d.poster.avif?t=1771944935\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/be688b0e77450707749a3504d717641d.webm?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/be688b0e77450707749a3504d717641d.mp4?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/8de8fefce8cc9c0ecc266ecb49bcd344.avif?t=1771944935\" width=320 height=64 /></span><br>We have prepared eight room types for players to discover. Different room types have their own advantages, and players can choose freely according to their preferences.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/5ffd232806e625ce7ab7a573ada66fbe.poster.avif?t=1771944935\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/5ffd232806e625ce7ab7a573ada66fbe.webm?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/5ffd232806e625ce7ab7a573ada66fbe.mp4?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/4b582ace5748bee3f3c766dd065ee8f2.avif?t=1771944935\" width=320 height=64 /></span><br>Everyone knows that the winter in the Arctic is very cold, but the Arctic still has its own unique four seasons. We simulate the weather and temperature of the four seasons in the Arctic, as well as their corresponding gameplay, such as: controlling room humidity in summer and managing room temperature in winter, RVs that can be rented in spring, summer and autumn, and Arctic igloos in winter.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/aba0a519eeb4e6199abca3dd4b144b7c.poster.avif?t=1771944935\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/aba0a519eeb4e6199abca3dd4b144b7c.webm?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/aba0a519eeb4e6199abca3dd4b144b7c.mp4?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/7b985d73e62f41ca0b4de58fe8e9258c.avif?t=1771944935\" width=320 height=64 /></span><br>There are many wild animals in the Arctic, so legal hunting is allowed in many places. In the game, players can hunt legally in the winter hunting season. There are also several types of guns available in the game, and players can choose their favorite guns for hunting. Winter Arctic specialty recipes are also one of the purposes of hunting.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/b6a26040ab3cf8a0fa98531e236a76b5.poster.avif?t=1771944935\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/b6a26040ab3cf8a0fa98531e236a76b5.webm?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/b6a26040ab3cf8a0fa98531e236a76b5.mp4?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/e9b9b76cdbd4132bc6b1414336710cbf.avif?t=1771944935\" width=320 height=64 /></span><br>Expanding a business can never rely on just one person. In the game, players can hire employees and special agents to expand the business of the motel. Players can train employees and arrange their work according to different focuses.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/127d60370c030198b8856b170ae9d104.poster.avif?t=1771944935\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/127d60370c030198b8856b170ae9d104.webm?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/127d60370c030198b8856b170ae9d104.mp4?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/bc75039d3b01f82ce2d07ea913d68d29.avif?t=1771944935\" width=320 height=64 /></span><br>The game is full of various random events, such as traveler partners investigating cheating, police patrolling your motel, health inspections, stranger events, etc. And due to insufficient police presence in the Arctic, the police also need your help in arresting wanted criminals.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/41bfde406750038aff2d110b07c0ced2.poster.avif?t=1771944935\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/41bfde406750038aff2d110b07c0ced2.webm?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3098470/extras/41bfde406750038aff2d110b07c0ced2.mp4?t=1771944935\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
